author: AP
title: Virus-caused unemployment in tennis could lead some to quit
description: Some professional tennis players and coaches are having a hard time financially right now because of the coronavirus pandemic
content:
Like plenty of people from all walks of life, 26-year-old Mitchell Krueger wants to sign up for unemployment benefits to make up for income lost because of the coronavirus pandemic.
